When to Use Salesforce Interactions Web SDK If Using Marketing Cloud Personalization and Data Cloud

Salesforce Interactions Web SDK can be used in Data Cloud but also if you’re using Data Cloud, Marketing Cloud Personalization (formerly Interaction Studio), or both Data Cloud and Marketing Cloud Personalization. If you’re transitioning from Data Cloud to Marketing Cloud Personalization, update your Salesforce Interactions Web SDK configuration. When you update the configuration, you can send data to Marketing Cloud Personalization only and use the Marketing Cloud Personalization connector to ingest data into Data Cloud.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in:

The table shows when Salesforce Interactions Web SDK is used and depends on your use of Data Cloud and Marketing Cloud Personalization connector:

PRODUCTS USED	USE
Marketing Cloud Personalization Only	Salesforce Interactions Web SDK
Data Cloud Only	Salesforce Interactions Web SDK
Data Cloud and Marketing Cloud Personalization	Marketing Cloud Personalization connector
The transition from Data Cloud to Marketing Cloud Personalization	To send data to Marketing Cloud Personalization only, update the Salesforce Interactions Web SDK configuration. The Marketing Cloud Personalization connector creates data streams.
